    <h1>Reach (Social)</h1>
    <p class="description">The total number of <strong>unique users</strong> who see your social media content — each person counted once, regardless of how many times they're exposed to it. The cleanest measure of your actual audience size.</p>
    <div class="post-meta">
      <div class="meta-author">
        <div class="meta-avatar">AVR</div>
        <div class="meta-author-info">
          <span class="meta-author-name"><a href="/authors/akshay-vr/">Akshay VR</a></span>
