              <span class="faq-toggle"><svg viewBox="0 0 12 12"><path d="M6 1v10M1 6h10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/></svg></span>
            </button>
            <div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>Reach counts each unique person once, no matter how many times they see your post. Impressions count every single view, including repeat views by the same person. A post with 1,000 reach and 3,000 impressions means each person saw it an average of 3 times.</p></div></div>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-item">
            <button class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
